  "prompt": "How do you know if you have a crush on someone?",
  "response": "Here are some common signs that you might have a crush on someone:\n\n1. Physical and emotional signs:\n- You get nervous or butterflies around them\n- You frequently think about them\n- You want to look your best when they're around\n- Your heart races when they're near\n- You pay extra attention to their social media\n\n2. Behavioral signs:\n- You try to spend more time with them\n- You laugh at their jokes, even if they're not that funny\n- You want to impress them\n- You get jealous when they interact with others\n- You find reasons to talk to or text them\n\n3. Emotional signs:\n- You feel happy when they're around\n- You're interested in learning more about them\n- You daydream about potential romantic scenarios\n- You feel a strong attraction beyond friendship\n- You want their approval and attention\n\n4. Psychological signs:\n- You idealize them and see them in a very positive light\n- You fantasize about a potential relationship\n- You feel a strong emotional connection\n- You want to share personal details with them\n\nRemember, everyone experiences crushes differently, and these signs can vary from person to person.",
